data.description: Fabulous almost new home located in Pike TWSHP! This 3bedroom 2full bath home has new flooring, new lighting, new cabinets in kitchen, new coutertops, new bathroom vanitys, new HVAC system. Lots of updates done here and no expense spared. All appliances stay! Enjoy watching TV on your brand new 42inch flat screen TV! Located close to virtually everything, and easy access to 465. A wonderful neighborhood to live in- this home is situated in a culdesac and backs up to woods. So no one behind you!
